{"tid":2517449,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"日本coffee shop抱怨毒撚入店聖地巡禮有損品牌形象","createTime":"2021-05-05T10:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T10:22:21.000Z","uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d721c1dbcf9ae91247014c6aee95c7e4ab89f077","tid":2517449,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:19:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.toy-people.com/?p=61676_01\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D61676_01&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn4hk9ljSbOzVJb7ECUhiv3w%3D&h=6cd7d054\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.toy-people.com/?p=61676_01</a><br />\n<br />\n位於東京青山的一間知名咖啡廳，為日本知名多媒體企劃作品《Love Live! Superstar!!》在動畫中角色澁谷香音（澁谷 かのん） 家的原型，因此吸引不少粉絲前往聖地巡禮，不論是店外拍照還是入店用餐等行為。最近被人發現店長在個人推特上對於這個現象抱怨，主要針對這些動漫粉絲的「入侵」感到反感，也引起 5ch 上的日本鄉民討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/162010482916.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F162010482916.png&h=e8d3000d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼ 參考的原設計圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/162010524938.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F162010524938.png&h=0cbbc11e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼《Love Live! Superstar!!》角色澁谷香音（澁谷 かのん）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/162010789535.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F162010789535.png&h=cc7d246c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於不少《Love Live! 》 粉絲前去該店朝聖，多數攜帶相關的的周邊商品在店內用餐，有些許的人甚至會以 Cosplay 的裝扮入店消費。<br />\n<br />\n▼ 推特上粉絲前去聖地巡禮的圖片<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/162010629923.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F162010629923.png&h=30f4e8c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/162010636371.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F162010636371.png&h=27398290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/16201063953.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F16201063953.png&h=04ae4396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/162010643519.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F162010643519.png&h=8f17d525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/16201064507.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F16201064507.png&h=f974fd2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"110a8bbf9943f7ea01729a6560238749e8f00799","tid":2517449,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:19:10.000Z","msg":"不過這樣的現象引起店長不滿，在私人推特上抱怨，<strong><ins>認為動畫跟本店的風格不合，雖然這些粉絲並沒有做出逾矩或是造成他人困擾的行為。但因為該店開設在青山，原本客群多為流行服飾業界的人士、模特兒與音樂創作者等，這些人打扮多較為時尚，而動漫粉絲前來人數的增加認為會產生有損咖啡店的品牌形象的顧慮。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n▼ 店長個人在推特上的抱怨<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/162010690260.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F162010690260.png&h=11a8df51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/162010694495.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F162010694495.png&h=3b361d21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/162010692713.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F162010692713.png&h=4503c7fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n店長也有提到其實店鋪人氣已經滿不錯了，不需要動畫拉抬，在該地也頗有名氣，<strong>有時實在無法負荷突然增加的動漫粉絲消費者，要是有怪人前來消費也會讓店內評價受損</strong>。以該店菜單來看，的確是以精緻的西式餐點為主，或許店長對於自身所鎖定的客群與前來的動漫粉絲有所不同，才會產生這樣的抱怨。<br />\n<br />\n▼ 該店的菜單<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/162010713153.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F162010713153.png&h=0fe5960e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/162010715164.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F162010715164.png&h=d4186991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/162010716063.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F162010716063.png&h=a8fd6db7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/16201071667.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F16201071667.png&h=8babdf8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果店長的這些發言導致炎上，5ch 上諸多網民表示前去的粉絲既然沒做出逾矩的行為，也沒造成店內其他消費者困擾，店長何必如此貶低這些前去巡禮又在店內消費的粉絲呢 ? 也讓店長個人推特被網民灌爆，目前處於暫時關閉的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n這樣的現象也讓滿多網民驚訝，其實日本對於 ACG 文化已經接受度比起其他國家更高了，甚至原形設計參考應該都有與店家溝通過才採用的，沒想到巡禮現象超出店家的預期，還是讓店家產生抱怨。或許未來有相關合作時，店家應該考慮清楚自己對於店鋪的定位或是合適度再行合作，這樣的抱怨讓粉絲網民炎上也是在所難免的...。"},{"pid":"d1c9eb5d62be532f1eb37a439baf8242786af92d","tid":2517449,"uid":46389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:21:28.000Z","msg":"生意好左都屌<br />\n洗唔洗咁有性格"},{"pid":"bce4919ab3d2476d87893b274f5641bd58cf538a","tid":2517449,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:22:21.000Z","msg":"食屎啦 on9店長"}]}